# Campaign		a major multi-year research activity with a discreet purpose
# Date		date on which sampling occured
# Treatment		main experimental treatment
# Replicate		replicate block
# Station		replicate station
# Species		crop species collected
# Fraction		a specified component of total plant (or sample) biomass
# Biomass
#        DATA TABLE CORRECTIONS AND COMMENTS
#2011-10-6 sven bohm. Discovered that in 2004 wheat grain was coded as a species with the fraction WHOLE rather than as wheat with the fraction SEED. Corrected by updating the crop_biomass table.

#2012-1-31 Sven Bohm. It is likely that in 2003 soybeans were not threshed due their greenness and small size. I found a comment in the log book that indicated that the threshing was unsuccessful but no further indication as to the final outcome.

#2011-12-21. Sven Bohm. Added an entry for the whole plant to the pre 2003 data where previously we had reported only the grain and the stover. This makes it easier to compute total biomass over the study period since the 'WHOLE' fraction can be used during all years.
